column12: For wluna, there is a clearly visible drop in price after some negative events, so could be good to visualise
For ustc there are 2 negative events one after another in which the price drops massively
Basically negative events might result in big falls but positive events rarely result in large raises.
With dai, it's not super visible but the lines of best fit do show the expected trends, wouldn't probably use it though on its own
Could possibly be good to showcase how different the changes might look - in some cases it's drastic and in others more minor
